---

<main class="govuk-width-container" role="main" id="main">
  <%= partial "shared/support/breadcrumbs", locals: { page: "Connect a Mac, iMac or Macbook" } %>
  <div class="govuk-main-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
      <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
        <%= partial '/shared/support/_sidebar' %>
      </div>

      <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Connect to GovWifi using a Mac, iMac or Macbook</h1>
        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Instructions</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">Once you have a GovWifi <%= link_to "username and password", "/about-govwifi/connect-to-govwifi", class: "govuk-link" %>, follow the steps below. Depending on your device, you may need to scroll down to see all the fields.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 1 - Select the wifi icon at the top right of your screen.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 2 - Select <strong>GovWifi</strong>.</p>
        <%= image_tag "troubleshooting/mac-os-step-2.jpg", class: "img-fluid" %>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 3 - Enter the GovWifi username and password you received by email or text message.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Your password is case sensitive. It's 3 words without spaces. The first letter of each word is capitalised.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 4 - Select <strong>Join</strong>. You will be asked to confirm the network is genuine by checking the certificate.</p>
        <%= image_tag "troubleshooting/mac-os-step-4.jpg", class: "img-fluid" %>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 5 - Select <strong>Show Certificate.</strong></p>
        <%= image_tag "troubleshooting/mac-os-step-5.jpg", class: "govuk-!-width-full" %>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 6 - Check that the certificate is called <strong>wifi.service.gov.uk</strong> and it's issued by the <strong>GeoTrust DV SSL SHA256 CA.</strong></p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 7 - If so, select <strong>Continue</strong>.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Step 8 - Your device will ask you for your computer password to save these settings. This is the password you normally use to sign into your computer.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">You should now be connected to GovWifi.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
